dead marine
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an empty pint (beer) bottle; very common in NZ for `empty liquor bottle' (esp. after a party) from the 1870s;  see beer shell.
Origin:[none]
Register: informal

Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
